name: Eyeverse
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: The EYE token is intended to be used mainly within the ecosystem of Eye Labs and its projects (Mainly Eyeverse & Eye.watch), the  holders of Eyeverse NFTS will get staking rewards in the form of $EYE that can be used for future Mints & Claims.
